NOTE:You MUST have SDL2 to compile this game. If you don't have it first get
	mercurial, then follow the README in the "lib" directory.

How to build the Game:
Go into the src/ directory, and either execute "./build.sh" or type:
make

The go back into the main directory and run the game.
cd ../
./poc
